{"tid":547003,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"信報簡卓峰號稱波浪大師、開班授徒，恆指成個圖180度改變數浪方式","createTime":"2018-02-01T04:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T04:39:24.000Z","uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cca1767ee75b64b2a6e84aead1e17456c9ee10b6","tid":547003,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2018年2月1日</span><br />\n簡卓峰 突圍而出<br />\n道指10天線失守利淡 港股提防見頂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/investment/article/1758483/%E9%81%93%E6%8C%8710%E5%A4%A9%E7%B7%9A%E5%A4%B1%E5%AE%88%E5%88%A9%E6%B7%A1+%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E6%8F%90%E9%98%B2%E8%A6%8B%E9%A0%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Finvestment%2Farticle%2F1758483%2F%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%258C%258710%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%25B7%25A1%2B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25A6%258B%25E9%25A0%2582&d=tKULNKj27C%2FG92dllZ2ZRDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2cb21227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/investment/article/1758483/%E9%81%93%E6%8C%8710%E5%A4%A9%E7%B7%9A%E5%A4%B1%E5%AE%88%E5%88%A9%E6%B7%A1+%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E6%8F%90%E9%98%B2%E8%A6%8B%E9%A0%82</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直接睇圖</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/02/01/1758483_ed7a59fde6699b9787c6598c629f9501_620.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F02%2F01%2F1758483_ed7a59fde6699b9787c6598c629f9501_620.png&h=a636dd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n======= 傳送門 ========<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2018年1月15日</span><br />\n[另一燈神] 恒指十年萬點上落 32000關前待變 - 簡卓峰 突圍而出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/529583/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/529583/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直接睇圖</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/01/15/1745159_c97da7773a7d307233ef963d504d4ee6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F1745159_c97da7773a7d307233ef963d504d4ee6.png&h=a906db5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ec8909cfc42b4a3a69092550f0a9425422524cb","tid":547003,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:39:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">補充資料</span><br />\n<br />\n請問簡卓峰何時會道歉？<br />\n2017年08月10日 12:03 (其他)<br />\n<br />\n簡卓峰先生在2016-08-18的信報發表題目為：道指升軌失守 恒指黃昏之星2浪見頂。<br />\n<br />\n文中寫道:現在，標指又創新高，形成更大的喇叭形頂， 9RSI及MACD又頂背馳，MACD熊差距，預料蓄勢大跌逾50%，反映港股絕非牛市已重臨，但如果港股日後出現牛市，本欄會認錯及致歉。<br />\n<br />\n由當天至今天，簡生也持續看淡，我想請問，簡生何時會道歉？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下是簡生一年來發表的文章題目：<br />\n<br />\n2016-10-05<br />\n恒指9月射擊之星 長和似形成頭肩頂<br />\n<br />\n2016-10-20<br />\n恒指中行日經似大小頭肩頂<br />\n<br />\n2016-11-14<br />\n恒指頭肩頂（3）浪尋底<br />\n<br />\n2017-02-28<br />\n道指11連升覓頂 匯控失守升軌尋底<br />\n<br />\n2017-03-28<br />\n道指七連跌 港股雙頭告急<br />\n<br />\n2017-06-19<br />\n恒指2浪後抽完成 展開3浪跌市<br />\n<br />\n2017-07-05<br />\n港股10年一災 7月黃昏之星啟動<br />\n<br />\n2017-07-10<br />\n恒指2浪見頂 3浪尋底至明秋<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://forum.hkej.com/node/143847-%E8%AB%8B%E5%95%8F%E7%B0%A1%E5%8D%93%E5%B3%B0%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E6%9C%83%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkej.com%2Fnode%2F143847-%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%2595%258F%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589%25EF%25BC%259F&d=tKULNKj27C%2FG92dllZ2ZRDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e8c2fc3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkej.com/node/143847-%E8%AB%8B%E5%95%8F%E7%B0%A1%E5%8D%93%E5%B3%B0%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E6%9C%83%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%EF%BC%9F</a>"}]}